<paragraph id="EB80A1C79F7F35CE8D2929DDECB855D5" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">Vulpius-Scharte</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="22779C1807548649F55E3ED31F3626CB" pageId="null" pageNumber="435" type="description">
<paragraph id="6BFFBE53E334D02D4894F57B5F45710F" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="9CA75B99629399703C109BE1C83EA81A" class="Polychaeta" family="Asteraceae" genus="Serratula" kingdom="Animalia" order="Asterales" pageId="null" pageNumber="435" phylum="Annelida" rank="species" species="tinctoria">
<emphasis id="803A7BEDC3696023A530DB5A9537C08B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">S. tinctoria</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 2) durch folgende Merkmale: 10-40 cm hoch; 
<emphasis id="D30A19B04665D0964F13CECD2035791C" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">
<normalizedToken id="5B24603F85D7C1D7EF3560AA625DB22F" originalValue="Köpfe" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">Koepfe</normalizedToken>
zu 2
</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="E35BB850DC323B0EEF97A54E37C18B83" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">
5. Kopfig 
<normalizedToken id="6D58A0F86C75E05C4C2FFCD2A29F9FD9" originalValue="genähert" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">genaehert</normalizedToken>
; 
<normalizedToken id="AB138E7CABE98A37F0B465902B2B1EB2" originalValue="Hülle" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">Huelle</normalizedToken>
der 
<normalizedToken id="B3664A4401F2766FDB108ED44244B45F" originalValue="blühenden" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">bluehenden</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="F099999E2FE87657C5F6E9873EAB2904" originalValue="Köpfe" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">Koepfe</normalizedToken>
1,4
</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="7B1E4331B842B9B8467C2ACE258E5F5F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">1</emphasis>
, 
<emphasis id="6DDDE53969705A8616A572E2F092E45B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">7 cm lang und in der Mitte 0,6</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="44C270F986419990BE4790A36CA690CD" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">
1,2 cm dick, 
<normalizedToken id="016D8A02C2B1D08FEABBA8A81E40D6EC" originalValue="Hülle" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">Huelle</normalizedToken>
bei noch nicht 
<normalizedToken id="A5397A2A71697A4C8D2ADCCAD0E23545" originalValue="blühenden" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">bluehenden</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="8AFCE560CB6B55DC46906F7598F3F158" originalValue="Köpfen" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">Koepfen</normalizedToken>
kugelig; 
<normalizedToken id="4E2FEAB6309A9607BFA44438185CAC1E" originalValue="äußere" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">aeussere</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="3860EA499D22426B4A408D5BC7669B04" originalValue="Hüllblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">Huellblaetter</normalizedToken>
2
</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="A129B9E654F86BF79118EC79DCD8304A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">2,5 mm breit;</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="47FDAC8BF3E59ABC29B74A693146C5B3" originalValue="Blüten" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">Blueten</normalizedToken>
meist ⚥. - 
<normalizedToken id="728F7330A5DFE741941C30E7230B6CF3" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="85A9877048A985CB927E7ED5117B6167" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">
<emphasis id="E1AA82F59CE82652CAF8E6047F25B6DC" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">Zytologische Angaben.</emphasis>
Keine Untersuchungen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="070880D27A3B700B5437BFCC4C45C989" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">
<emphasis id="6A94681E2F010BC025606BFDC3BDA387" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">Standort.</emphasis>
Subalpin, seltener alpin. 
<normalizedToken id="EC51C986D1C4246660CD9BDF662E044F" originalValue="Mäßig" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">Maessig</normalizedToken>
feuchte, kalk- und tonreiche 
<normalizedToken id="971FCB9F4F9C01A6185AA14B780CF723" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">Boeden</normalizedToken>
an steilen, sonnigen 
<normalizedToken id="2A927C346FDD64407958181E58CBED66" originalValue="Hängen" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">Haengen</normalizedToken>
. Wiesen, lichte 
<normalizedToken id="F3ACBEDDDAF2988D4562068092792237" originalValue="Wälder" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">Waelder</normalizedToken>
. 
<emphasis id="A45FFB8E6F3FC77E1CB5DED0625BA4E8" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">Serratulo-Caricetum sempervirentis</emphasis>
Berset 1969.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="2CFCA1FBD458EAD765B7A42C347DC818" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">
<emphasis id="160090F14A00ED948CD3D0D32D2EDB8E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">
Verbreitung. Mittel- und 
<normalizedToken id="7BEC730B25A7EDA9EEE383F364DD071D" originalValue="südeuropäische" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">suedeuropaeische</normalizedToken>
Gebirgspflanze
</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="9A042C634E694892FFB4EA99EBE7D527" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">westlich</emphasis>
)
<emphasis id="C430871C4CBD185F2577CDC0052E7B97" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">:</emphasis>
Nordspanische Gebirge, 
<normalizedToken id="CB5766F5305B0B38511FADD347943A56" originalValue="Pyrenäen" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">Pyrenaeen</normalizedToken>
, Plateau Central, 
<normalizedToken id="0AF7EE33A40B0B7F92F9DA187FBA3699" originalValue="Südvogesen" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">Suedvogesen</normalizedToken>
, Jura, 
<normalizedToken id="C9C228950450030ECA0B80BC3C941294" originalValue="Süd-" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">Sued-</normalizedToken>
und Westalpen, Liechtenstein, Karawanken, Nordapennin (
<normalizedToken id="2A8D0329333F20371402CA9EEAB2216E" originalValue="südwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">suedwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Toskana). - Im Gebiet: Westliche Kalkalpen (nord- und 
<normalizedToken id="A5E2923130E46782D2B8B40043557F72" originalValue="ostwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">ostwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis zur Dent de Valerette im Wallis und zur Dent de Brenlaire im Kt. Freiburg), 
<normalizedToken id="E7E9E86634FC0957F39B79AE9DAF86EA" originalValue="südlicher" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">suedlicher</normalizedToken>
Jura (
<normalizedToken id="F9960D5023FEE702A484205661E21222" originalValue="nordostwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">nordostwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis zur 
<normalizedToken id="CF36F287BEA6EED1C8C3D2207696BB6F" originalValue="Dôle" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">Dole</normalizedToken>
und La Chaux-de-Fonds), 
<normalizedToken id="B1DCA203D8857B25506B8CB2034DD447" originalValue="Südvogesen" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">Suedvogesen</normalizedToken>
(Rotenbach bis Hohneck; Reisberg), Liechtenstein (von H. Seitter 1969 an der Mittagsspitze entdeckt; die bei Murr 1923 unter 
<taxonomicName id="7C4541E23746ACC50B2DE0374ABF1CBE" class="Polychaeta" family="Asteraceae" genus="Serratula" kingdom="Animalia" order="Asterales" pageId="null" pageNumber="435" phylum="Annelida" rank="species" species="tinctoria">
<emphasis id="4F25F43D79AECCCEAF414E1FB1E35CFF" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">S. tinctoria</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken id="34050BF58A801F0394362CA3417BE287" originalValue="aufgeführten" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">aufgefuehrten</normalizedToken>
Fundorte Planken-Gafadura und 
<normalizedToken id="211D8995B0D9315D10A0D23F113B8B3F" originalValue="Münz" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">Muenz</normalizedToken>
beziehen sich wahrscheinlich auch auf 
<taxonomicName id="F3D955B2449CA220810632BA14EC78C2" class="Polychaeta" family="Asteraceae" genus="Serratula" kingdom="Animalia" order="Asterales" pageId="null" pageNumber="435" phylum="Annelida" rank="species" species="vulpii">
<emphasis id="42E538626B0889D8BD83056AB518BE65" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">S. Vulpii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
), 
<normalizedToken id="5BF71FB304A232FF2AF002C7762D5CCA" originalValue="südliches" pageId="null" pageNumber="435">suedliches</normalizedToken>
Tessin (Generoso), Comerseegebiet (Grigna).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
